name: FLIP SKIZZ #12
description:
When an alien virus infected the world humans and machines bonded. We escaped into the virtual world to fight for our existence. This is new URTH an original series featuring an array of original characters. FLIP SKIZZ is a one monster army. He charges into the fray head first, tossing adversaries into his chomping gut. 

By holding a character from this series you will be eligible for secret airdrops into your wallet. Collect all of the characters for the chance to receive the entire comic when it is released.
